Iron Fist

Powers up punching moves.

Affected Moves

The following moves are affected by this ability.

Name Type Category PP Power Accuracy Description
Bullet Punch 30 40 100 The target is struck by tough punches as fast as bullets. This move always goes first.
Comet Punch 15 18 85 The target is hit with a flurry of punches that strike two to five times in a row.
Crabhammer 10 100 90 The target is hammered with a large pincer. Critical hits land more easily.
Dizzy Punch 10 70 100 The target is hit with rhythmically launched punches and may be left confused.
Double Iron Bash 5 60 100 The user strikes with its arms twice in a row. This may also make the target flinch.
Drain Punch 10 75 100 An energy-draining punch. The user's HP is restored by half the damage taken by the target.
Dynamic Punch 5 100 50 The user punches the target with full power. This confuses the target if it hits.
Fire Punch 15 75 100 The target is punched with a fiery fist. This may also leave the target with a burn.
Focus Punch 20 150 100 The user focuses its mind before launching a punch. It fails if the user is hit first.
Hammer Arm 10 100 90 The user swings and hits with its strong, heavy fist. It lowers the user's Speed, however.
Headlong Rush 5 120 100 The user executes a full-body tackle. It also lower's the user's Def and Sp. Def.
Ice Hammer 10 100 90 The user swings and hits with its strong, heavy fist. It lowers the user's Speed, however.
Ice Punch 15 75 100 The target is punched with an icy fist. This may also leave the target with frostbite.
Jet Punch 15 60 100 The user summons a torrent to punch at blinding speed. This move always goes first.
Mach Punch 30 40 100 The user throws a punch at blinding speed. This move always goes first.
Mega Punch 20 80 85 The target is slugged by a punch thrown with muscle-packed power.
Meteor Mash 10 90 90 The user hits the target with a punch fired like a meteor. This may also raise its Attack stat.
Plasma Fists 15 100 100 The user fights with electrified fists, making Normal-type moves Electric-type.
Power-Up Punch 20 40 100 Striking opponents makes the user's fists harder. Hitting a target raises the Attack stat.
Rage Fist 10 50 100 The user attacks with rage. Its power increases the more hits the user has taken.
Shadow Punch 20 60 — The user throws a punch from the shadows. This attack never misses.
Sky Uppercut 15 85 90 The user attacks the target with an uppercut thrown skyward with force.
Surging Strikes 5 25 100 The user strikes thrice with a flowing motion. This alttack always results in a critical hit.
Thunder Punch 15 75 100 The target is punched with an electrified fist. This may also leave the target paralyzed.
Wicked Blow 5 80 100 The user strikes the target with a fierce blow. This attack always results in a critical hit.
